#include <bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
#include<string.h>
void swap (char *x, char *y)
{
    char temp;
    temp = *x;
    *x = *y;
    *y = temp;
}

void permute(char *str, int i, int n)
{
   int j;
   if (i == n){
     printf("%s\n",str);

   }
   else
   {
        for (j = i; j <= n; j++)
       {
          swap((str+i), (str+j));
          permute(str, i+1, n);
          swap((str+i), (str+j)); //backtrack
       }
   }
}
